</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[189,1399,1498,1562]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
Red Sea: Suez Canal (
<bibRefCitation author="Schellenberg A." box="[453,673,1498,1524]" journalOrPublisher="Transactions of the Zoological Society of London" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" pagination="633 - 692" part="22" publicationUrl="10.1111/j.1096-3642.1928.tb00209.x" refString="Schellenberg A. 1928. Report on the Amphipoda. Zool. Res. Cambridge Exp. to the Suez Canal, 1924, XXXV. Transactions of the Zoological Society of London 22: 633 - 692. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1096 - 3642.1928. tb 00209. x" title="Report on the Amphipoda. Zool. Res. Cambridge Exp. to the Suez Canal, 1924, XXXV" type="journal article" year="1928">Schellenberg 1928</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Monod T." box="[688,840,1498,1524]" journalOrPublisher="Gruvel dans le Canal de Suez: Crustaces I. M e moires de l'institut d'Egypte" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" pagination="1 - 19" part="34" refString="Monod T. 1937. Missions A. Gruvel dans le Canal de Suez: Crustaces I. M e moires de l'institut d'Egypte 34: 1 - 19." title="Missions A" type="journal article" year="1937">Monod 1937</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Barnard K. H." box="[855,1081,1498,1524]" journalOrPublisher="British Museum (Natural History) Scientific Reports" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" pagination="131 - 209" part="4" refString="Barnard K. H. 1937. Amphipoda. John Murray Exp. 1933 - 34. British Museum (Natural History) Scientific Reports 4 (6): 131 - 209." title="Amphipoda. John Murray Exp. 1933 - 34" type="journal article" year="1937">K.H. Barnard 1937</bibRefCitation>
); Museri Island off Eritrea (
<bibRefCitation author="Ruffo S." box="[199,333,1535,1561]" journalOrPublisher="Terzo contributo alla conocenza degli Anfipodi del Mar Rosso. Memorie del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Verona" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" pagination="1 - 77" part="17" refString="Ruffo S. 1969. Study sui Crostacei Anfipodi LXXVII. Terzo contributo alla conocenza degli Anfipodi del Mar Rosso. Memorie del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Verona 17: 1 - 77." title="Study sui Crostacei Anfipodi LXXVII" type="journal article" year="1969">Ruffo 1969</bibRefCitation>
); Port Sudan (present study).
</paragraph>
